icle/.highlight/aipac-aoc-and-the-american-lefts-antisemitism-problem/00000190-1280-d667-abf0-76cbd3740000</link><description>指责民主党众议员亚历山大·奥卡西奥-科尔特斯是 AIPAC 的傀儡，这或许是美国左翼人士迷失方向的最可笑的例子。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:58:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-13/ty-article/.highlight/aipac-aoc-and-the-american-lefts-antisemitism-problem/00000190-1280-d667-abf0-76cbd3740000</guid></item></channel></rss>